		<title>Suggested Reading: Top 5 Victorian novels every steampunk must read.</title>
		<link>https://clockworktwist.com/blog/2014/04/20/suggested-reading-top-5-victorian-novels-every-steampunk-must-read/</link>
					<comments>https://clockworktwist.com/blog/2014/04/20/suggested-reading-top-5-victorian-novels-every-steampunk-must-read/#comments</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[]]></dc:creator>
